   <concept id="FAR_32_501_5" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">32.501-5</ph> Other protective terms.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">If the contracting officer considers it necessary for protection of the Government’s interest, protective terms such as the following may be used in addition to the Progress Payments clause of the contract:</p>
         <ol id="d2086e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2111e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Personal or corporate guarantees.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2111e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Subordinations or standbys of indebtedness.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2111e22">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            Special bank accounts.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2111e27">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            Protective covenants of the kinds in paragraph (p) of the clause at <xref href="52.232-12.dita#FAR_52_232_12"
                        base="i1049607"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.232-12</xref>, Advance Payments.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2111e35">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
						            A provision, included in the solicitation and resultant contract when first article testing is required (see <xref href="Subpart_9.3.dita#FAR_Subpart_9_3"
                        base="i1115649"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  9.3</xref>), limiting progress payments on first article work by a stated amount or percentage.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
